    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName key="#Wine"><name ref="Gariberga">Gariburga</name></persName> del fu
                                <persName><name ref="Everardus">Everardo</name></persName> di
                            <placeName ref="#places/1595">Levizzano Rangone</placeName>, col
                        consenso del suo <rs key="#Advocatus">avvocato</rs>
                        <persName key="#Advocatus"><name ref="Teudebrandus">Teoprando</name></persName>, vende alla
                        <rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di <orgName key="#Wine #Prevosts #Deacons #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1107">S. Martino</orgName> di <placeName key="#Churches"
                                ref="#places/1590">Cozzano</placeName>, nella persona di <persName key="#Prevosts #Deacons"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs> e <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs>, tutti
                        i suoi beni, tra cui delle <rs key="#Wine">vigne</rs>, al <rs key="#Price"
                            >prezzo</rs> di sedici soldi. Il detto prezzo «fuit misso directus da
                        pars predicta ecclesie Sancti Martini et Petroni diacono ad ipsum precium
                        dandum nomine <persName key="#Medical_doctors"><name ref="Natale">Natale</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Medical_doctors">medicus</rs>». ... «Signo + manu suprascripti
                        Gariburgi vinditrice qui fieri rogavit, cui relectum est. Signo + manu
                        suprascripti Teoprandi [advoca]tor[e eius suprascripti] Gariburgi qui eidem
                        consensit et manu sua posuit. Signo +++++ manibus <persName key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus #Witness"><name
                            ref="Robertus">Roperti</name></persName> et <persName key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus #Witness"><name
                                ref="Damianus">Damiani</name></persName> et <persName key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus #Witness"><name
                                    ref="Rainbertus">Ragiverti</name></persName> et <persName key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus #Witness"><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName> [et ..5.. vir devotus] <rs
                            key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">vir devotus</rs>, vir devotus, vir
                        devotus, vir devotus rogatis <rs key="#Witness">testis</rs>. + <rs
                            key="#Writer">Scripta</rs> cartula vindicioni per manu <persName key="#Notary #Writer"><name
                                ref="Gisbertus">Giseverti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> p[ostra]dicta co[n]plevit et dedit et
                        roboratam ad testibus tradic[ta conplevit] et dedit et coram testibus
                        relegebit».</ab>
                </div>
